    "Details": "Over a third of the Mandrill's tonnage is devoted to a pair of LRM-20 launchers and their attendant ammunition, which is limited, but usually enough for duels. The head-mounted ER small laser is something of an afterthought, though it does allow Mandrills to keep fighting after they run out of ammo.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Laser</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
