  "StockRole": "Missile Boat",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Mandrill was the first of the totem 'Mechs created. Designed to resemble its namesake animal, the Mandrill is clearly a Clan Fire Mandrill design, and was the last gasp of a united Mandrill Clan before it became hopelessly fragmented into its various Kindraa. Hoping to recapture some of that spirit, Khan Amanda Carrol ordered Kindraa Sainze to produce new Mandrills in 3058, the first in over a century, which was originally a Kindraa Payne design. She also ordered the Kindraa to trade the 'Mech to other Kindraa so that the totem 'Mech is present in each.",
